text: The Monte Carlo Classic is a yearly female professional squash tournament in Monte Carlo, Monaco. In its current version, it is part of the PSA World Tour. In recent times it has been held in November or December each year. The prize money is usually $25K, but there have been some exceptions over the years. ==Results== {| class="wikitable" style="font-size:88%" |-
